---
title: Sri Lankan Fish Curry with Green Beans and Cardamom Rice
description: We think that if you can cook a delicious meal without creating mountains of washing up, then you’re onto a winner. This recipe is just that. Simple, quick, and packed with delicate, fresh flavours, Mimi’s Sri Lankan inspired fish curry is a dish you’ll be recreating time and time again. And if you find it hard to get perfectly fluffy rice every time, the trick in tonight’s recipe is about to change that. You can thank us later.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sri-lankan-fish-curry-125e4a63-b6b355c8.jpg
